Sumber mengatakan

00:29:53.799 --> 00:29:55.480
dia telah menutup studionya

00:29:55.480 --> 00:29:57.279
dan sedang mengerjakan seri baru

00:29:57.279 --> 00:29:58.880
karya seni instalasi.

